<subSubSection pageId="76" pageNumber="784" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="76.[191,1400,714,1299]" pageId="76" pageNumber="784">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[191,426,911,944]" pageId="76" pageNumber="784">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Forrest's Rock Squirrel is diurnal and appears active throughout the year.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
